      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_255cfabb8ba9e04ffa08a91a",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "html",
        "text_hash": "e5e239560bc125a20ff2ac1fea50915bc198dd4f5b5256ec447a8a71e00132b3",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_32f81c9463b640c9aadd5248"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_ce767a0ad7f401837b35e538",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "Item One\n   Item Two\n   Item Three",
        "text_hash": "2d6220767e8535a5bf22a21b5882188f424f1ece79c57823a91dc45a19d53aef",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_32f81c9463b640c9aadd5248"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_fe7b235901c1c8d959c0f204",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "[!NOTE]\n属性也在被清除的物件变为网格物件的时候失效，所以你应该在一个会变成网格布局的布局上，加上被清除的尾部。",
        "text_hash": "5ce826cdce94c7b48b2f349ce018ed6811e7cd062fbcf005a562abb3a9f36bbe",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_32f81c9463b640c9aadd5248"
      },
      "type": "quotation"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_9da62cebe1feae5ca6687952",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "回滚方式",
        "text_hash": "a6e4fa5fbab779a212da49bff5b109a42e025ad26eb9fef9b7fa14bfc23bda97",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_32f81c9463b640c9aadd5248"
      },
      "type": "heading"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_c79c2aafa48edc182f809816",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "有很多布局方式，它们同这个浮动示例使用的方式是类似的。你可以选择能够与你需要建立的布局范式符合得最好的那个。",
        "text_hash": "0736897ec94051af1c5aa7e5497952f66284c47837709927bd51f28d6e5594b0",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_32f81c9463b640c9aadd5248"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_1f8e31fd8403e573e12a08e4",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "浮动和**清除**\n  - : 如上所示，如果浮动和清除的物件变成了弹性或网格物件，浮动和清除属性不再影响布局。\ndisplay: inline-block\n  - : 这种方式能被用来建立列布局，如果一个物件被设为display: inline-block，但是之后变成了弹性或者网格物件，inline-block 行为将会被忽略。\ndisplay: table\n  - : 这种在这几节课的介绍中描述的建立 CSS 表格的方式可以被用作回滚。被设为 CSS 表格布局的物件将会在它们变为弹性或者网格物件的时候不再表现出这种行为。重要的是，被建立起来用于修复表格结构的匿名盒子没有被建立起来。\nMultiple-column Layout\n  - : 对于某些布局，你能用multi-col作为回滚。如果你的容器有任何一个column-*属性被定义，之后变成了网格容器，那么多列行为不会实现。\n作为网格的回滚的弹性盒\n  - : 弹性盒由于受到了 IE10 和 IE11 的支持，比网格有着更好的浏览器支持。不过，在这节课的稍后部分，你一定要看下旧浏览器对弹性盒相当参差不齐而且令人困惑的支持的相关信息。如果你把弹性容器做成了网格容器，任何应用到子元素的flex属性都会被忽略。",
        "text_hash": "ccce7999cdd08d25a449464a43d0a87eb58608b2a52a770d0aaf204ae2b51e16",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_32f81c9463b640c9aadd5248"
      },
      "type": "unordered_list"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_1b621ed8db7ae25cea8e38cf",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "对于许多在旧浏览器中微调的布局来说，你可能会发现你能用这种方式使用 CSS，给访客亲切的体验。我们加入了一个更简单的基于旧的和受到良好支持技术的布局，然后用新一些的 CSS 建立一个可以由 90% 的用户看到的布局。但是存在这样的情况：回滚代码会需要包含新浏览器也能理解的东西；举例来说就是，我们要往我们的浮动物件中加入百分数宽度，从而让列看起来更像网格，拉伸以充满容器。",
        "text_hash": "0f16fa745cac0bc773b4f337430a350079c5a7a2add158ac06d8a2a8d8e132be",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_32f81c9463b640c9aadd5248"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_274408fa1ecd2c52fb6fe33b",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "在浮动布局中，百分数是依照容器计算的——33.333% 是容器宽度的三分之一。但在网格中，这 33.333% 是根据物件所在的网格区域计算的，所以只要网格布局引入进来，物件的大小实际上变成了我们想要的大小的三分之一。",
        "text_hash": "08c6e366847976fcfcfa6bdfe5ffc586be1ccd8404dc6910c2e3d4d9008ef9f9",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_32f81c9463b640c9aadd5248"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_9719de7fb2c35139b43af62f",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "css\n{\n  box-sizing: border-box;\n}",
        "text_hash": "aef3c27e0d63aac99d3b397c37a0f83e9049fcd094e2a2948c64b4c7c54b763e",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_32f81c9463b640c9aadd5248"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_d6c49ecbc4a584e051b9cd23",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": ".wrapper {\n  background-color: rgb(79, 185, 227);\n  padding: 10px;\n  max-width: 400px;\n  display: grid;\n  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;\n}",
        "text_hash": "231d81d7a6948d80b67d4f32afbbf6de9fba6d6ee65885943cc2973ee4ee4cf3",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_32f81c9463b640c9aadd5248"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_198531e504f92cdc9b3ed53c",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": ".item {\n  float: left;\n  border-radius: 5px;\n  background-color: rgb(207, 232, 220);\n  padding: 1em;\n  width: 33.333%;\n}",
        "text_hash": "d2450793902207719490bde078ac6ace88dd44ab3e731a385cb540b4fb1a0e5e",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_32f81c9463b640c9aadd5248"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_d9e8d7759e3600126c99cc31",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "html",
        "text_hash": "e5e239560bc125a20ff2ac1fea50915bc198dd4f5b5256ec447a8a71e00132b3",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_32f81c9463b640c9aadd5248"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_3d9f2780bc58b124b0bef6d0",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "Item One\n   Item Two\n   Item Three",
        "text_hash": "2d6220767e8535a5bf22a21b5882188f424f1ece79c57823a91dc45a19d53aef",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_32f81c9463b640c9aadd5248"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_817da2e7f98f43777e62b437",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "为了处理这种问题，我们需要有能够探测网格是否受到支持的方法，也就是探测它是否会覆写宽度的方法。CSS 在这里为我们提供了一个解决方法。",
        "text_hash": "0b1ba609d1b5bc20b47806f07b597f6c53e480d252aa933108c62df04cf5048b",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_32f81c9463b640c9aadd5248"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_aae406829647e5e437e44c12",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "特性查询",
        "text_hash": "3e441d9bdbcb08c6625c0073e35186663839200e4173bcb3cff0bfb37487414c",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_32f81c9463b640c9aadd5248"
      },
      "type": "heading"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_586b6dc085fff61b203b3789",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "特性查询允许你测试一个浏览器是否支持任何特定的一个 CSS 特性。这就是说，你可以写一些面向不支持某项特性的浏览器的 CSS，然后检查以了解浏览器是否支持，如果支持的话就可以加进你的复杂布局了。",
        "text_hash": "8477431798d85f877e0bc0a4ac95d5f77c23717f78f65a0067bc71bb8d4317a6",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_32f81c9463b640c9aadd5248"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_0f1c1d1ac33bf5cae2f965f1",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "如果我们向上面的示例中加入了一条特征查询，要是我们知道网格受到支持的话，我们可以用它把我们的物件宽度设定回auto。",
        "text_hash": "2744990eaaf2bc385fd2ac0440b47d8c9ba717e958b5e40b5025d5af5d00c3d7",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_32f81c9463b640c9aadd5248"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_aecf59f6393e3f7a94df2345",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "css\n{\n  box-sizing: border-box;\n}",
        "text_hash": "aef3c27e0d63aac99d3b397c37a0f83e9049fcd094e2a2948c64b4c7c54b763e",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_32f81c9463b640c9aadd5248"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_d97f231d1cb530df819359c3",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": ".wrapper {\n  background-color: rgb(79, 185, 227);\n  padding: 10px;\n  max-width: 400px;\n  display: grid;\n  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;\n}",
        "text_hash": "231d81d7a6948d80b67d4f32afbbf6de9fba6d6ee65885943cc2973ee4ee4cf3",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_32f81c9463b640c9aadd5248"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_b5bf0128133e77eef2ebe2d8",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": ".item {\n  float: left;\n  border-radius: 5px;\n  background-color: rgb(207, 232, 220);\n  padding: 1em;\n  width: 33.333%;\n}",
        "text_hash": "d2450793902207719490bde078ac6ace88dd44ab3e731a385cb540b4fb1a0e5e",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_32f81c9463b640c9aadd5248"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_60ac30246930c51f19aa7d58",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "@supports (display: grid) {\n  .item {\n    width: auto;\n  }\n}",
        "text_hash": "4d7e1d1fc2916812854e811a9c3b0426749420127b580323628093c6f6569226",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_32f81c9463b640c9aadd5248"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_308420e57f3189ed623ef049",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "html",
        "text_hash": "e5e239560bc125a20ff2ac1fea50915bc198dd4f5b5256ec447a8a71e00132b3",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_32f81c9463b640c9aadd5248"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_b500c91a3b794ca0a3e9955b",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "Item One\n   Item Two\n   Item Three",
        "text_hash": "2d6220767e8535a5bf22a21b5882188f424f1ece79c57823a91dc45a19d53aef",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_32f81c9463b640c9aadd5248"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_1158f243bebf27fcc1f7d153",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "对特性查询的支持，在各现代浏览器中都是很好的。但是你应该注意那些既不支持 CSS 网格，也不支持特征查询的浏览器。这就是说在上面详细介绍的一种方式，对这些浏览器而言，会表现得很好。我们要做的是，先在任何特性查询以外，编写我们的旧 CSS。不支持网格也不支持特性查询的浏览器会使用这部分它们可以理解的布局信息，将其他东西全都忽略掉。支持特性查询和 CSS 网格等的浏览器会运行网格代码和特性查询之内的代码。",
        "text_hash": "d672c08e15fffc7ccae8e4cd038fc8bcd91460260e2991a7f38ba340765ff1b8",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_32f81c9463b640c9aadd5248"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_13a6cc7cc0396b0451dc21c1",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "对于特性查询的规范，也包含了测试浏览器是否支持某个特性的能力——这只在浏览器支持特性查询的时候有用。未来，一种检测支持的缺失的方式将会实现，同时不支持特性查询的浏览器也将退出历史舞台。但是现在，你要使用这种编写旧 CSS 的方式，然后覆写它，以求最广泛的支持。",
        "text_hash": "b47d34893fddc7c4712c77e4a11736b8bbadcd5ab5b1f99615e09c4984748701",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_32f81c9463b640c9aadd5248"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_a322e15d64ba484c824e64e1",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "测试旧浏览器",
        "text_hash": "3d3d836efb74c5d3215d10a78ac945fdbdaa17ee0338016b5792bca6ff72cadb",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_32f81c9463b640c9aadd5248"
      },
      "type": "heading"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_33659d574a465cc48674b7a8",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "一种方式是使用在线的测试工具，例如 Sauce Labs，在跨浏览器测试模块里有详细说明。",
        "text_hash": "ccb5ead8533ad049fd5be70b370368e3d84053534c652df29375cc24e6afd66a",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_32f81c9463b640c9aadd5248"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_4bf93b054b4a688c9c0d4b25",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "总结",
        "text_hash": "04830193b408eeb17c18cfb88440e68061423af6e0c2944c79e4c4cfc6a0f0dc",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_32f81c9463b640c9aadd5248"
      },
      "type": "heading"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_0cb1298542008218f9d5c40e",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "你现在有了自信地使用例如网格和弹性盒技术、建立面向旧浏览器的回滚以及利用任何可能会在未来出现的 新技术所需的知识。",
        "text_hash": "f3ee5300711eaf8c75d2a1b51fc0a6495f4dff46961e3bcd4ebddbb762840f7b",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_32f81c9463b640c9aadd5248"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_c3185bdb0d78f19e4a59ad83",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "参见",
        "text_hash": "d27f89055b790f219353b4388307a138320ad4c9f05b64b170c43a2969c7e89c",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_32f81c9463b640c9aadd5248"
      },
      "type": "heading"
    },
    {
